snippet.title: Little Magic SNES SFC Walkthrough (Stage 1 - 6)
snippet.description:
As of now there's only one walkthrough for this game on GameFAQ's and it stops at Stage 78. Since I figure a text-based walkthrough for this game is near impossible to follow, I decided to make a video walkthrough. I'm just throwing this together real fast, so it isn't perfect. 

edit: Someone made a TAS speedrun for the game. Consider this to be your complete walkthrough: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ih4cZn7mQ-Y
